ategory/Ring/Basic.html#CommRingCat\">CommRingCat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `X ⟶ Spec A` is a morphism of schemes, then `Spec` of `specTargetImage f` is the\nscheme-theoretic image of `f` and `f` factors as\n`specTargetImageFactorization f ≫ Spec.map (specTargetImageRingHom f)`\n(see `specTargetImageFactorization_comp`). ","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/AffineScheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.specTargetImage","kind":"def","line":1183,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.specTargetImage","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/AffineScheme.lean#L1183-L1188"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/AffineScheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.specTargetImageIdeal\"><span class=\"name\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>.<span class=\"name\">specTargetImageIdeal</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">X</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme\">Scheme</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">A</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Category/Ring/Basic.html#CommRingCat\">CommRingCat</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\">X</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Combinatorics/Quiver/Basic.html#Quiver.Hom\">⟶</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Spec\">Spec</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/RingTheory/Ideal/Defs.html#Ideal\">Ideal</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">A</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `X ⟶ Spec A` is a mo